Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:06.98,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}笑顔を忘れたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.56,0:23:12.09,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}苦しむすれ違う世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:19.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}争いと偽りの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:26.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}心　枯らすのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:33.79,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}荒れ狂う波に浮かぶ花のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:41.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Lead the way　嵐を乗り越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:48.54,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}枯れ行く大地を踏みしめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:59.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Go ahead　まっすぐ歩み出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.21,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Loneliness
